This is a list of [[wikipedia:Player_versus_player|player-versus-player]] (PvP) worlds for VRChat. Player-versus-player worlds are multiplayer [[:Category:Game worlds|game worlds]] that will pit users against each other, to compete for a chance to win a match, round, game, or set. Player-versus-player games may involve team collaboration, strategy, and usage of powerups or weapons to meet the win conditions of a game.
